            "description": "Returns 202 Accepted with { requestId, sessionId }. The agent response is POSTed to `callbackBaseUrl` with HMAC-signed headers. Stand up a receiver (e.g., `requestbin` or a local Express server) and set `callbackBaseUrl` to its address during provisioning to observe the callback."
